strings:
<voice_0x010008EF><se_low>Yangus: Crikey!
I dunno wot the old codger's on about sometimes!
<voice_0x010008F0><se_low>Yangus: Sounds to me like we 'ave to find that Rylus geezer, right? So wot we waitin' for!?

<voice_0x010008F1><se_low>Yangus: I s'pose we'd better do wot 'e says.
Shall we get goin' then, guv?
<voice_0x010008EC><se_low>Yangus: You weren't thinkin' of goin' wivout me, I 'ope!
<voice_0x010008ED><se_low>Yangus: I'm the best there is when it comes to lookin' for people. It's my ‘piece of resistance’, innit.
